00:34:56,834 --> 00:34:58,778
to your intravenous
nutrient bottles. Why?

310
00:34:59,527 --> 00:35:02,599
I don't need them.
They make me feel sick.

311
00:35:03,326 --> 00:35:04,965
I don't understand.

312
00:35:05,767 --> 00:35:09,202
- They've got to be your only
source of food. - They're not

