444
00:50:28,785 --> 00:50:31,534
<i>At the police station in Camelford,
Kathy Draper talked to</i>

445
00:50:31,558 --> 00:50:34,840
<i>Quebec Bureau of Health official
Claude Lapointe.</i>

446
00:50:36,331 --> 00:50:40,359
<i>This is not just a question of swine flu
